# DEP.KEYSTONE

Deterministic dependency verification and SBOM attestation engine.

## Initial Scope

Supported inputs:
- requirements.txt
- package-lock.json
- Cargo.lock

Outputs:
- normalized dependency graph
- sbom.cdx.json
- verification-report.json
- evidence.sha256

## Status

Early build under Logos Governance Systems Inc.
